    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Feast in the calendar of several Christian denominations, observed on August 6. It celebrates an episode in the New Testament in which Jesus is metamorphosed into a radiant in glory upon a mountain.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
